  "texts": [
    "Additionally, all evaluation metrics were normalized across the experiments to ensure consistency and facilitate comparative analysis.",
    "ModelsIn this study, we conducted experiments using different open-source LLMs due to their accessibility, reproducibility and flexibility for adaptation across various tasks.",
    "Open-source models are also more resource-efficient than closed-source models, which often entail significant financial costs for deployment.",
    "With open-source models, we maintain transparency and scalability while avoiding the prohibitive overhead of closed-source systems.",
    "OPTOPT [28] is an open pre-trained transformer language model released by Meta AI."
  ]
